accessibility.text: After the \"welcome\" voice, the pure green world starts changing. You just stand there, vacuously, alone, watching everything changing around you. Strangely there is every negative emotions filling in your heart, except for sadness.

The jellyfishes gradually vanish into the fog far away from you. It is hard to tell the distance because there is no objects as references, but something else is getting closer to you from another side.

When they get close out of the fog, bouncing and rolling funnily, you can finally see their appearance. They are a group of giant balloon-like creatures, with incredibly big holes on the place of mouth of their body.
